<div id="outline-container-orgc3c6efb" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgc3c6efb">Main research interest</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgc3c6efb">
<p>
Maitre de Conférences HDR (i.e. <i>Assistant Professor</i>) at the Université
Paris-Sud XI, I'm a reseacher at <a href="http://www.limsi.fr/">LIMSI-CNRS</a> in
the <a href="http://www.limsi.fr/Scientifique/tlp/">Spoken Language Processing
group</a>.
</p>

<p>
<b>Research topics:</b> Machine learning and Natural Language Processing, Deep Learning, Machine Translation, Statistical language modeling, Automatic Speech Recognition.
</p>
</div>
</div>

